# ── CS of Doom — environment ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Google Gemini API key for the AI tutor + free-text answer grading.
# Used ONLY in server route handlers (app/api/*). Never shipped to the client.
# Create one (free tier) at https://aistudio.google.com/apikey  •  do NOT commit it.
GEMINI_API_KEY=

# Optional model overrides. Leave blank to use the app's built-in defaults
# (gemini-2.5-flash for the conversational tutor, gemini-2.5-flash-lite for
# cheap inline grading).
# GEMINI_TUTOR_MODEL=
# GEMINI_GRADER_MODEL=

# ── Cross-device sync (Firestore) ─────────────────────────────────────────
# Shared family access code that gates /api/progress. When SET, the app syncs
# progress to Firestore so the learner's laptop + phone and the parent view
# share one record. When BLANK, sync is OFF and the app is local-only
# (localStorage), exactly as before. Each device enters this code once.
# On Cloud Run this is injected from the FAMILY_ACCESS_CODE secret.
FAMILY_ACCESS_CODE=

# Firestore document id for the single learner (collection "learners").
# Defaults to "tom"; change only if you host more than one learner.
# LEARNER_DOC_ID=tom
